"content": "<h2>Actual mirrors</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job37:18\">JOB 37:18</a></strong> <em>Mirrored glass was unknown in ancient times. Metal mirrors gave an adequate though imperfect reflection.</em> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod38:8\">EXO 38:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa3:23\">ISA 3:23</a></p>\n<h2>Mirrors illustrating human attitudes</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas1:23-Jas1:25\">JAS 1:23–1:25</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov27:19\">PRO 27:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor3:18\">2CO 3:18</a></p>\n<h2>Mirrors illustrating an imperfect human view of God</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor13:12\">1CO 13:12</a></strong></p>",
